	  			<h4>1lb of Jacobs Wonderbar<span class="pull-right">$7.00</span></h4>
	  			<p class="help-block">Dark Roast Blends<span class="pull-right help-block">Value $14.95</span></p>
	  			<div class="row">
	  				<div class="col-md-10">
	  					<p>named in honor of philz only son jacob. each memorable sip boasts delicious layers of nuts and chocolate filled with a full-bodied flavor and finished without any acidity or bitterness. jacobs wonderbar brew is a dark roast favorite!</p>
	  				</div>
	  				<div class="col-md-2">
	  					<button class="btn btn-success pull-right">Buy!</button>
	  				</div>
	  			</div>
	  		</div>
	  	</div>
	  	<% if current_user && current_user.businesses.include?(@business) %>
	  	  <%= link_to "Edit Your Business", edit_business_path(@business), class: "btn btn-default form-control" %>
	  	<% end %>
